The '''Guardian Tower''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It increases the Defensive Value of a limited number of Guardians by 100%. If there are not enough Guardians in the city, City Guards can take their place and gain the same bonus. These towers don't count towards a city's building number limit.

Requirements: [[Town Hall]] Level 6

